research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Knox City, Texas, include the Mayor and five Council Members. Jane Ann Bosworth also holds the designation of Mayor Pro Tem. There was a slight discrepancy in one council member's name, with 'Albert Magana' being used based on the official city website and Texas State Directory, while 'Chuco Magana' appeared in other sources. Council members are designated as 'at-large'.
